CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 31, 1959, pg. A16 reads: "Marie Jeanne will model some of her own exquisite creations at the fashion show Nov. 6 at the A. Leo Weil School, sponsored by members of the young Women's Board of Ushers of Wesley Center AME Zion Church. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: "Marie Jeanne" Mary Jane Shipman Brown modeling fur hat, and fur trimmed wrap-around top, standing against light colored wall
